\id GAL NT0004.GA - SUENA NT - Wilson 11-JUN-87 
\h Galata 
\toc1 PAS PAULO MENI GALATA EMA DUBURE GAENUA 
\toc2 Galata 
\mt1 PAS PAULO MENI GALATA EMA DUBURE GAENUA  
\ip \it Paulo meni pas ei awa Tuara dubu Galata provins amira noisowa amire gaenua. Gita Paulo meni nusokare nana noisonua. Pas emira susu ego ewa: Yuda ema eni meni Yesura ge niniro amire Mosera lo ge awa susumuro puro noise ema ge ninai dapikarago da ago warise toisowa. Are Paulo meni opi nusokare puro osisinoise pas ei awa gaenua. Ego ine senua awa: Nakai Yesu tuma diro amire Mosera lo ge dipinoise ewanana inowenakai, awa opi awa. Nakai tuma diaira daba ewanana inowenakai. \it*  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Na Paulo meni ge ei awa gainona. Na aposolo nowena, ata ema meni oko iyetiwa, o ema zo meni namore bua ge oko senua. Awa Yesu Kristo, Anutu Mama meni betaira ena awa-uzenu seka wenua, nuto Mamere ami bua ge awa namore sewato awa.  
\v 2 Na ata otao mamai eni namore dai nowera nakare ami dubu Galata provinsra nowewa nimorekare pas ei awa potitinonakare awa.   
\p
\v 3 Anutu Mama ata Tua nasokai Yesu Kristo amira nana ena dumi yagabare duba-ozaire semu nisokare nana niro itaise.  
\v 4 Yesu nu Mama nasokai Anutura ge dipinoise nakai zebura nuai waya amira ena soero pumamu sero waya nasokai emo nuai nuso donua awa.  
\v 5 Are Anutu bowi wai gege wai awa itai gege itaise. Iyo.   
\s1 Zo nu Oziga Ewanana zo ewe samunoya ami niaora gegenai wamunoya.  
\p
\v 6 Nikare Anutu meni Kristora dumi yagabara potitinoise uzumunu numore dai nowewa ami be iboi tepo noko eya nu doro Oziga Ewanana zo ewe ami emo dana zaawinowa giro di tainitinona.  
\v 7 Ota Oziga Ewanana zo itita? Tepo awa. Ata ema eni meni duba nisokare sisinoise Kristora Oziga Ewanana sara ewe waise inowera, awa gege itia.  
\v 8 Are nanekareta utura angelo zo meni Oziga Ewanana kereninakare awa doro ewe samunoya, nu awa niaora gegenai waise.  
\v 9 Ge gita senakare da awa noko tona ewa. Zo nu Oziga Ewanana niniwa awa doro ewe samunoya, nu awa niaora gegenai waise.  
\v 10 Agoro ge tona ei awa ema meni namore gara kokopai waise tonita? Tepo awa. Anutu meni namore gai kokopai waise tona awa. Na emara nana koinitinoise bua inuamena sia, awa na Kristora bua mai oko wero nuamena.   
\s1 Paulora nuai amira ge.  
\p
\v 11 Otao mamai naso, na ge sana niniu. Oziga Ewanana tugata wena niniwa awa zebu emara oko aewa.  
\v 12 Na emara nana ena oko pumuna, o ema meni na oko sero gipero awewa. Yesu Kristo nu nutope namore kereninua awa.  
\v 13 Na gita Yuda emara nana dubura noise tani inoise noisona awa nikare niniwa awa. Na Anutura dubu doise-gaise awinoisona awa.  
\v 14 Ago inoise babezinoma nasokarera ge awa osai azu toise zewai-zawai wero otao mamai naso dainina awa.   
\p
\v 15 Ata Anutu nu na miera nana tinira ena bua nuso emo gegeninua, are ginu te wenu dumi yagaba nusora na uzumunua.  
\v 16 Ago wero Mai nusora Oziga Ewanana ema Yudakora nana ena tugata wanise sero Maira susu awa namore kereninua. Ago wenu be amire na ema eni oko atata wena.  
\v 17 Ota na eriro witi Yerusalem nate niro erama gita aposolo bua zaawero noisowa awa gamu oko witina. Ata na Arabia zebura baro nomite Damaskas nate ewesemuna awa.   
\s1 Paulo meni Yerusalem nate witiro noisonua.  
\p
\v 18 Ago noina zepa etorobara tepo wenu na Sifas gamu sero Yerusalem witiro waiko be 15 numore dai noisona.  
\v 19 Be amire na aposolo eni kaka gamu wena. Ata Tua Yesura nami kiaka Yakobo awa gege gina awa.  
\v 20 Ge gainona awa Anutura giti mokara me toise gainona.  
\v 21 Ata ama na Siria ata Silisia zebura baro noisona awa.  
\v 22 Ata be amire Kristora dubu Yudaya zebura noisowa ami benau naso kaka gamu inoisowa.  
\v 23 Nukare oziga ge naso gege ego niniwa awa, “Nakai doise-gaise awinoise Kristora ge sisinoisonua ami zeme ge sisamu inoisonua awa tugata inoise nowia.”  
\v 24 Ago toise susu naso giro Anutu bowi inoise yawa sara wewa awa.   
\c 2  
\s1 Paulo meni Yerusalem ena aposolo eni tamuro ge uge wenu niniwa.  
\p
\v 1 Ago noina zepa 14 tepo wenu nato Banabare Yerusalem noko witamu sero Tito pumuro eroma witinakare awa.  
\v 2 Awa tepo oko wena. Tua meni ge namore kereninu giro witina. Witiro ema giti kopi zazo bowire ami bua i-tupewena awa gara me amu ine wago wai azu, nukare gege itiwa amire Oziga Ewanana ema Yudakora nana ena tugata inowena awa kereniro uge wena awa.  
\v 3-5 Agoro bua nasokarera mokara ena ema eni meni esega wero ge ninai meni nuago inoise nakai Yesu Kristore tairo Mosera lo ge tepo nowenakai amira susu tamamu sero dubu nasokare nana toiro uma wewa. Nunekare ami nakai Yudara lo ge amira muire noko nuanisekai towera. Are ema ami nakare puro osamu sewa nakare Oziga Ewanana meni nisokare nana itai gege itaise zewai wero daininakare awa. Ago wenakare namore dai noisonua Tito nu Grik ema, ata ema giti kopi meni ge nasokare niniwa te wenu Tito tama aiso nuso kapaise kaka samu wewa.   
\s1 Aposolo eni nukare Paulora bua giwa te wenua.  
\p
\v 6 Ota ema giti kopi asai awa nukare zazo bowire nusokare neni? Nukare osaita witai amira ge tepo asinona. Anutu meni emara zazo oko kotupitinowia. Ema giti kopi ami ge seka zo oko namore susumuwa.  
\v 7 Tepo awa. Nukare ego ine giwa awa: Anutu meni Petoro Yuda emara nana Oziga Ewanana sero sero awaise senua, da ago ine na ema Yudakora nana sero sero awanise senua awa.  
\v 8 Ago inoise Petoro aposolo bua Yuda nana waise Anutu nu sorepisia, da ago ine Anutu meni na soremi bua naso ema Yudako dubura nana ena wisena awa.  
\v 9 Tua bua namore potinua awa Yakoboto Sifasre ata Yohane nukare Yesura dubura giti kopi noisowa ami giro baitiwa. Are nukare nato Banabare otao inoise wana ziwa awa. Ago wero nato ema Yudakora nana bua inuanato nukare nutopekare Yuda dubura nana bua wamu sewa awa.  
\v 10 Ago inoise bogamasa dubu nusokare nana mokara nowera awa soremanisekare gege sewa. Na emokore bua awa wamu yaba inowena awa.   
\s1 Paulo meni Petorora susu kereninua.  
\p
\v 11 Ama Sifas meni Antiok nate muro tani wenu waya wenu giro na nu giti mokara gaero senena. Awa nera kota, nu opi wenua.  
\v 12 Nu gita ema Yudako eni meni tama aiso kapai tepo ge ou gutero noiwa amire dai ma eroma be dara potiro ninoisowa. Ago inoiwa Yesura dubu Yerusalem itewera amira giti kopi Yakobo ami ema eni iyetinu Antiok ema dubura susu gamu baro kei awewa. Baro kei awewa Petoro nukare giro azu wenua. Azu inoise opi ego wenua awa. Nukare nu gara Yudara lo ge dai ema wago wai azu, nu ema Yudako ge ou gutewa awa doro gago-giago awenua awa.  
\v 13 Opi inoise dubu zora nana baro noko dubu zora nana baro awenu Yuda ema eni nu giro da ago wewa. Ago wewa Banaba dai nusokare nana susumuro da ago wenua awa.  
\v 14 Nukare Oziga Ewananara ebata sonero kaka patamu wewa giro na ema enira nana giti mokara ena Sifasre ego sena awa, “Ni Yuda ema meni Yuda emara nuai amira kota, ema Yudakora nuai amira nowesa ami nogoro ema Yudako awa uzumasa Yuda emara nuai amira nuarise towesi?” Ago sena awa.   
\s1 Zo nu Yesu tuma diamunoya ami ema saramai wero nuamunoya.  
\p
\v 15 Nakai ema Yudako pasina inoise nowera nukare ago ine oko kei awenakai. Nakai Yuda ema kei awenakai awa.  
\v 16 Ata nakai ego gosinowenakai awa: Zo nu lo ge dipinowia nu awa kota, zo nu Yesu Kristo tuma didinowia nu awa Anutu meni ema saramai asinowia awa. Nakai ema saramai wamu sero giro lo ge dimai bua nasokai amira kota, Kristo tuma diai nasokai amira nakai Yuda ema dai Yesu Kristo tuma didinoise nowenakai awa. Ago inowenakai, nera kota, lo ge dimai bua meni ema wai saramai ine oko itia.  
\v 17 Nakai Yuda ema meni ema saramai wamu sero Kristo tuma didinowenakai. Nakai ami tuma diaire gege noise pasina ema wero nowenakai, ago Yuda ema meni towera, awa giro nogo samunonikai? Kristo meni nakai uzumawi pasinare wero nowenakai. Ago samunonikaita? Tepo awa.  
\v 18 Are nena gowena awa noko duero pamunona, awa na lo ge dai ema me nowena, awa nuai naso meni gatenamunoya.  
\v 19 Ata na lo ge dipinoe betero giro dona. Na Anutura nana nuamu ago wena. Are na noko lo ge dimaira biawa inoya.  
\v 20 Na Kristore dai ni pasinaira betena awa. Are nowena ei awa kotumai nasora kota, Kristo meni duba nasora nowia. Nuai zeme zebura nowena, awa Anutura Mai tuma didinoise nowena awa. Nune na emo dubara dumi pupinoise nuai nuso na emo donua awa.  
\v 21 Are na Anutura dumi yagaba awa oko azu towena. Lo ge dipinoise saramuro nuai itami sia, awa Kristo nu tepo zo betenua ago ine wamia.   
\c 3  
\s1 Lo gera ebata patiwa.  
\p
\v 1 O Galata ema dau. Nikare ai meni duba nisokare sisenu? Nakare Yesu Kristo ni pasinaira dewa amira uge dinakare giro baitiwa awa.  
\v 2 Na nena daimatara nikare atata wana seu. Nikare Ozana pumuwa awa nogo wero pumuu? Nikare lo ge dipinoise pumuuta ge niniro tuma diaire wero pumuu?  
\v 3 Duba dau nogoro inowewi? Nikare Ozanara putou meni bua zaawero inoe noko tamara putou meni bua awa pesunamu towita?  
\v 4 Ina putoura tani gita nisokare nana kei awenu giwa awa tepo kei awenuta? Kei awero me amu oko wenu, tanita.  
\v 5 Ata Anutu meni Ozana nimorekare potitinoise tani putoure nisokare nana inowia ami lo ge dimairata tuma diai nisokarera inowi?   
\s1 Abrahamra ebata patamunowa.  
\p
\v 6 Ge gayai zo ego itia awa niniwo, “Abraham nu Anutu tuma dinu giro Anutu meni nu ema saramai asenua awa.”  
\v 7 Are ego giu. Tuma diaire nowera ami Abrahamra saisibuna me awa.  
\v 8 Anutu meni ema Yudako nukare nu tuma diara giro ema saramai asamu emoko kotumuro Oziga Ewanana Abrahamre ego senu gaewa awa, “Ema dubu sero ami gawa nisora toiro pesunamunora awa.”  
\v 9 Are Abraham meni tuma dinu gawa nuso nana zamunua, da awa tuma diamunora ami gawa nusora toyamunora.   
\p
\v 10 Ata lo gera bua meni siwako nusokare wai nuamunora nukare awa waru dimamunora. Nera kota, ge gayai zo ego itia awa, “Lo ge denai itera awa zo oko dainawe. Zo nu lo ge zo dainamunoya ami waru dimamunoya.”  
\v 11 Are lo gera mokara noise Anutura nana ena pasina disai ine oko itia, awa ge ami sero kereniro poti damu nitinoya. Ata tuma diai emo inoise saramai wamunora ami nuai topetamunora awa.  
\v 12 Tuma diaira nuai amira susu zo, noko lo ge dimaira nuai awa susu zo. Nuto susu ewe, susu ewe. Lo ge dimaira nuai amira ge ego sai itia awa, “Zo nu lo ge dapikarago dimamunoya ami nuai topetamunoya awa.”   
\s1 Yesu nu nakai emo inoise waya nasokai dimunua.  
\p
\v 13 Ge gayai zo ego itia awa, “Ema nira ikokonai nukare awa warura seronai.” Are Kristo nu nakai emo inoise waru dimunua awa. Ago inoise nakai lo gera waru amira ena soenua awa.  
\v 14 Are Yesu Kristo emo Abrahamra gawa meni ema dubu giti amira nana te bayaise sero Yesu meni ago wenua. Awa Ozana namorekai sai awa tuma diaire wero panisekai sero ago wenua.   
\p
\v 15 Otao mamai, na ge awa ema zora potiro sane. Ema zo meni betinoise wau nuso maira asamunoya. Awa zo meni nu dainitinoise ge zo oko susumamunoya.  
\v 16 Ota nena Anutu meni potamu seroninua, awa Abraham ata mai nuso nuto amire sai awa. Mai awiso dainiro amire sai oko aewa. Awa daimatare sai. Awa Yesu Kristore sai awa.  
\v 17 Na ego emira tona awa. Anutu meni gita ge senu zewai wenu ama zepa 430 tepo wenu amire lo ge kereninua. Are lo ge ama kerenai ami nena gita potamu seroninua awa dai osai ine oko itia.  
\v 18 Nena potamu senu zewai wenua awa lo ge emo pai ine itami sia, awa seronai emo pai awa tepo wamia. Anutu meni seronai nuso awa dumi pumai nusora Abrahamre potinua awa.   
\s1 Lo ge awa zewai wero itai gege itaise sai oko aewa.  
\p
\v 19 Agoro lo ge nogoro kei awisi? Awa ge daira susu kei damu naise kei awisia. Ota itai gege itaise kota, Abrahamra sibuna, nu nena seronai amira mama ami kei awai amire lo ge dainaise sai awa. Lo ge awa angelora be meni senu ema zo zazo Mose ami Anutura nana ata eramara nana amira soe dopero pumuro ema bamere potinua awa.  
\v 20 Ema zo meni soe dopero dubu daimata kota, dubu eto awa sipunamu sero dopamunoya. Ata Anutu meni seronai nuso samu sero soe dopai ema zore oko senua. Nu nutope wenua.   
\s1 Lo ge meni nuai me ewanana tamai ine tepo.  
\p
\v 21 Lo ge meni Anutura seronai ge iwo inoita? Ago ine tepo awa. Lo ge meni nuai me ewanana nakai emo tamai ine tepo. Ago wai ine itami sia, awa me memeka me lo ge amira pasina disai awa kei awamia.  
\v 22 Tua meni senu gaewa awa ego itia, “Ema bama dapikarago pasinara benai sora itewera.” Awa nakai Yesu Kristo tuma diro nowenakai ami tuma diai nasokai amira gege seronaira me panisekai sero Anutura ge ago itia awa.   
\s1 Gita muire noisowa.  
\p
\v 23 Yuda ema nakai gita tuma diai tepo noinakai be amire lo ge meni nakai beninu muire iteye donakai tuma diaira bowi ge meni kei awero baitinua.  
\v 24 Agoro lo ge meni dia nasokai ine wero nakai Kristora nana potinua. Awa tuma diaire wero saramai wanisekai ago ine wenua awa.   
\s1 Tuma diaire wero Yesura mai awiso wenakai.  
\p
\v 25 Zeme nakai tuma diaira ebata kei awenu amira patinakai dia ema nasokai matu* amira mui kapenua.  
\v 26 Are nikare Yesu Kristo tuma didinowewa ami dapikarago Anutura mai matere bamere wero nowewa.  
\v 27 Nikare ge ou gutinoise Kristora nana susumuro Kristora te esa patitinoise nowewa.  
\v 28 Are Yuda ema ata ema Yudako, witaire osaire, emare bamere, ami zazaumuro nuai awa tepo wenu nikare dapikarago Kristo Yesura nana daimata wewa awa.  
\v 29 Nikare Kristora dubu wewa, are Abrahamra saisibuna me nowewa, are seronaira me puro nuamunowa awa.   
\c 4  
\s1 Nena wayara soumai meni Anutura mai awiso wenakai.  
\p
\v 1 Zo ego sana niniu. Mai zo nu mama betai mamera wau pamunoya ami mai morua noise mamera wau pai ine tepo. Nu soumai ine wero bazizinoise nuamunoya awa.  
\v 2 Mama meni mai baziro amire wau paise senua, are imo maita didikai meni wau nuso puro nuara mai bazai amire potara pamunoya.  
\v 3 Nasokai nana da ago ine itia. Gita duba meni mai morua ine noise zebura nena eure-taure* amira sou inoisonakai awa.  
\v 4 Ata ama be potai awa kei awenu Anutu meni Mai nuso iyetinu bama zora nana ena kei awenua. Kei awero Yudara lo ge sou wenua.  
\v 5 Awa nakai lo gera muira ena besai Anutura mai matere bamere wanisekai ago wenua awa.  
\v 6 Nakai mai matere bamere nuso wero nowenakai, are Anutu meni Mai nusora Ozana iyetawi osero duba nasokaira toiro ego zawa towia awa, “O Mama kokopai.”  
\v 7 Are nakai soumai nuso kota, mai nuso wero nowenakai awa. Are mai nuso noise Anutura dumi yagaba amira mama wero nowenakai awa.   
\s1 Nena me tepo nuwenai awa noko oko gawe.  
\p
\v 8 Ota nikare gita Anutu kaka gamu inoise tua ewe sou inoise noisowa. Tua awa nukare tua me oko aewa.  
\v 9 Ata zeme nikare Anutu giro baititinowewa. O ego sana te wae. Anutu nikare giro baititinowia awa. Are nena putou teporeta me amu awa nogoro noko kapeteniro sou wamu inowi?  
\v 10 Ago inoise waiko be eni, o inua eni, o pura eni, o zepa eni awa pura bamu asero de ike nitinowewa.  
\v 11 Ata bua naso meni awa nisokare nana me amu wai azu, na nikare emo kotumu-katumu dainiro inowena awa.   
\s1 Galata ema nukare Paulo nuwenamu sero wewa.  
\p
\v 12 O otao mamai naso, na nikare emo di toise amire sane. Na nikare ine wena, are nikare da ago na ine wewo. Nikare waya zo namore kaka wamu awa.  
\v 13 Nikare ninitinowa. Na gita yayare, are betata-batata inoise amire nikare Oziga Ewanana tugata wena.  
\v 14 Agoro yaya naso meni bua bamu nimorekare potina. Ata nikare namore biawa oko wewa. Na azu oko wewa. Tepo awa. Nikare na giwa Anutura angelo ine wena, o Kristo Yesu ine wena giro na uzumuwa.  
\v 15 Nikare be amire yawa sara wewa, awa nogoro tepo inoi? Nikare giti moka nisokare gusero namore potai ine te sia, awa ago wamewa, awa me gosinoise tona.  
\v 16 Agoro gita ge me tugata wena, are zeme nama gewa iwo nisokare ine inonita?  
\v 17 Ema eni awa ge uge nusokare meni nikare uzumara zaumurokai nikare nusokare nana bayawise kotumuro inowera. Opi sara nikare na doro nusokare nana bayawise inowera awa.  
\v 18 Nena ewanana emo uge wai awa ewanana. Awa na nisokare nana muro nuana amire gege kota, be giti wawa kokopai wamunoya awa.  
\v 19 Mai awiso naso, na nikare emo bama meni mai pumamu inoise yaya tapinowera ago ine tamuna, noko da awa tapinona. Agoro Kristo meni duba nisokarera kei awero baitaise yaya tapinoise nuamunona.  
\v 20 Na nuai nisokare giro itazaita inona. Are na nisokare nana muro pas meni kota, be naso meni nikare tugata wamu yaba inona awa.   
\s1 Sarara maire Hagara maire susu nusoto zora ewe, zora ewe.  
\p
\v 21 Atata wana seu. Nikare lo ge sou wamu inowewa ami lo ge gaya awa azipitinowewita?  
\v 22 Amira ana ge zo ego gayai itia awa. Abrahamra mai mata eto kei awewato, awa zo sou bama meni pumunua, zo ara nuso meni pumunua.  
\v 23 Sou bama meni pumunua nu awa emara kotumaira kei awenua. Bama nuso meni pumunua awa Anutura seronai ge amira kei awenua.  
\v 24 Are ge amira eniba ego itia awa. Bama eto ami Anuture tairo nuai ge eto awa etete wewato awa. Tairo nuai zo Sinai dirumura ena wewa, are dubu nuso meni sou bua wewa. Amira etete awa Abrahamra sou bama Haga meni wenua awa.  
\v 25 Sinai awa dirumu zo, Arabia zebura itia. Zazo nuso zo Haga. Yerusalem nata awa Sinai dirumure te inorato. Yerusalemra mai nukare Hagara mai ine soumai awa.  
\v 26 Ata Sara meni mui amu tairo nuai amira te. Ota Yerusalem nata zo utura itia ami nu soumai kota, nu lo gera mui amu. Nata ami mia me nasokai inoya.  
\v 27 Ge gayai zo ego itia awa,  
\li2 Bama eronai, ni mai kaka pamu nowesa ami yawa sara we. Mai pamu yaya tapinowera ago ine niso nana tepo, ni duba niso yawa sara waise. Bama emare amira mai etokaka kei awinuara bama eronaira mai awiso dainiro kei awamunora awa.  
\v 28 Otao mamai naso, Isaka nu Anutura seronaira kei awenua. Da ago ine nikare Anutura seronaira mai nuso kei awewa.  
\v 29 Ata gita mai emara kotumaira kei awai meni mai Ozanara kotumaira kei awai awa iwo wenua, da ago ine zeme itia.*  
\v 30 Are ge gayai nogo iti? Ego itia ewa,  
\li2 Soubama awa nu mai nusore dai tune bayareto.  
\li2 Soubamera mai meni bama mera mai amire dai mamera wau oko topetaise.   
\p
\v 31 Otao mamai naso, nakai sou bamera mai awiso tepo. Nakai bama mera mai awiso awa.   
\c 5  
\s1 Nakai mui besai meni noko oko muire wanekai.  
\p
\v 1 Nakai mui tepo nuanisekai Kristo meni mui besenua. Are eni meni nikare mui wero soumai nusokare* wawise sara zewai wero azu sewo.  
\v 2 Na Paulo meni sana niniu. Nikare saramai wamu sero tama aiso nisokare kaparise samunowa, awa Kristo meni nikare soremai ine te oko wamunoya.  
\v 3 Noko sero baitane. Zo nu Yudara lo zo dipinoise tama aiso nuso kapamunoya ami Yudara lo ge dapikarago dimai te wamunoya.  
\v 4 Ata lo ge dipinoise saramai nuamu towewa ami Kristore dai tairo nuai awa kapinowa. Awa-diai nuso dotewa, are nisokare nana me amu inoya.  
\v 5 Ata nanekare meni awa Ozanara putou meni tuma diai emo nuai saramai tamamu sero kotupitinoise nowenakare.  
\v 6 Kristo Yesure dai noise tama aiso kapaire nuaita tama aiso kapai tepo nuai awa nena me tepo awa. Ata tuma diaire dumi yagaba pumai awa nena me awa.   
\s1 Satanra muti meni gera sura oko osaise.  
\p
\v 7 Nikare gera ebata zaawero kokopai patiwa. Patitinoiwa ai meni ebata denu azenu ge me awa dotinowewi?  
\v 8 Anutu nikare uzupitinowia ami ge mera ebata oko gazinowia.  
\v 9 Wora muti pei-pai-mai-kaka ami ma sura baro te wero duamunoya, da ago ine ema waya daimata meni nikare dapikarago sisai waya wamunowa.  
\v 10 Nakai Tuare dai nowenakai, are nikare ge naso azu oko samunowa, awa gosinona. Are ema zota zo meni duba nisokare sisamunoya, amira ina nuso nana kei awamunoya.  
\v 11 Otao mamai, na nikare tama aiso kapawise tugata wamena sia, awa Yuda ema meni yaya bua naso nana tame oko potamera. Ata na nikare nuai seka tamamu tama aiso kapawise kaka samu inona. Nikare ni pasinaira gege nuai seka tamawise towena, are nukare yaya namore potitinowera.  
\v 12 Are duba nisokare sisinowera ami tama aiso nusokare azero kaparise tona awa.   
\s1 Mui tepo noise nena tebe-tabe wai tepo.  
\p
\v 13 Otao mamai, Anutu meni nikare mui amu nuawise uzumunua awa. Agoro mui amu nuai meni tamara nena amira ge dimawise kota, dubara dumi pupinoise sou ina-wa wawise nikare uzumunua awa.  
\v 14 Are Yudara lo ge dapikarago amira ge bamubake ego sai awa, “Ni nitope ara tapinowesa, da ago ine ema enire weyo.”  
\v 15 Nikare giro baitiu. Nikare ina-da wero ina-gaya wero awinoise nikare nitopekare dero tepo-tapo wanowa awa.   
\s1 Tebe-tabe nuaira mere Ozanara mere.  
\p
\v 16 Agoro ego ine tona awa. Nikare Ozanara uzumai ge awa ninitinoise noiwo. Ago inoise duba matura duba-duba oko wamunowa.  
\v 17 Duba matura ara tamai meni Ozanare iwo inowia. Noko Ozana meni duba mature iwo inowia. Ago wero nuto iwo ina-wa wawerato nikare nena wamu towewa awa wai ine tepo.  
\v 18 Ota Ozana meni nikare uzumai ninamunowa, awa lo ge meni nimorekare ema tua oko wamunoya.  
\v 19 Duba matura bua awa bezero oko itewia. Awa ego kei awinowia: kuma wai, tani waya wai, ge dai,  
\v 20 tua opi sou wai, kayo wai, iwo ina-wa wai, ge bawai, otao zore kotumai waya puro nuai, dumu wai, nena ziro soyai, zaumuro ewe-pape nuai,  
\v 21 duba-duba wai, ou zewai niro dau wai, ou zewai niro tani waya wai. Agoro nena eni-kani. Nena ago ine amira ge gita tugata wena, awa noko tugata wane. Ema pasina awa inowera ami Anutu imata Tua wero nowia amira natara oko toyamunora.   
\p
\v 22 Ozana meni me ego ine tamawi kei awinowia awa: dubara dumi pai, duba yawa sarare, bega puro nuai, awa-diaire, dumi yagaba, kora-makora wai, tani me gege inoise nuai,  
\v 23 saitiro nuai, duba meni sienitinoise nuai. Awa Ozana meni sawi me awa kei awinowia. Are lo ge meni nena me awa oko azu towia.  
\v 24 Kristo Yesura seronai nowenakai ami nuai matu nasokai duba-dubareta yaba waire awa ni pasinaira denakai tepo wenua awa.  
\v 25 Agoro Ozana meni nuai seka namorekai potinua, are Ozanara uzumai awa ninitinoise ebata nusora patanekai.  
\v 26 Nakai tama puro wititinoise oko ina-sa wanekai. Kotumai waya ina-wa oko wanekai.   
\c 6  
\s1 Otao mamai nasokai eni moure nuara giro soga wanekai.  
\p
\v 1 Otao mamai naso, ema zo meni betata wero pasina tamai giro nikare Ozanare meni saitiro nu kora wero pumuwo. Ago inoise etete naira ena betata wai azu, ni nitope uma we.  
\v 2 Nikare nena mou-mau awa soga ina-wa inoise dimuwo. Ago inoise Kristora lo ge te dimamunowa.  
\v 3 Ema osai zo meni nutope ema bamu asamunoya, awa nu nutope etete namunoya.  
\v 4 Nikare dapikarago da da ami nuai nikakare nisokare giro baitiwo. Ago wawa ewanana wamunoya, awa yawa sara ge awa ema zo emo kota, nikare emo wero kei awamunoya.  
\v 5 Buara mou awa mamere mamere wero pumuwo.  
\v 6 Yesura ge nikare tugata-magata inowera ema nukare ami emo nena ewa-gaewa nisokare nana itai giro potiwo.   
\s1 Noma nuai nasokaira me pamunonakai.  
\p
\v 7 Anutu etete nawa duwamunoi sia sero nitopekare oko etete nawe. We zo urasa me zo oko kei awamunoya. Noma we uretesa amira me gege kei awai pamunosa.  
\v 8 Zo nu duba matura we uramunoya ami noma duba matu nusora me pamunoya. Me awa betero yaya zewai-zawai tamai gege tamai. Ota zo nu Ozanara we uramunoya ami noma Ozanara me nuai me ewanana awa pamunoya.  
\v 9 Bua kokopai inoise biawa oko wanekai. Betata kaka wamu wamunonakai, awa noma me paira be nuso amire zamai bamubake pamunonakai.  
\v 10 Are be nasokai itia egore bere-bere ema dapikarago kora wanekai. Ago inoise otao mamai nasokai Tuara gera nowera amire dumi yagaba panekai.   
\s1 Paulo nu Kristora ni pasinai emo yawa sara wenua.  
\p
\v 11 Nikare owe bamubake wana naka naso meni gainona ei awa giu.  
\v 12 Yuda ema ge ou gutai eni meni nisokare nana noise tama nusokare puro witamu sero nikare tama aiso kapawise awita towera. Ne emo ago toweri? Susu nusokare ego ewa. Nukare Kristora ni pasinai tuma didinowera, ata nukare tama aiso kapai amira lo ge duara Yuda eni meni numorekare iwo wai azu, nikare dai tama aiso kapawise towera awa.  
\v 13 Tama aiso kapewa nukare awa lo ge oko dipinowera. Nukare awa ninekare tama aiso kapero nusokare nana susumawa tama nusokare bowi wamu sero towera awa.  
\v 14 Ota nane meni awa nena zota zo emo kota, Tua nasokai Yesu Kristo ni pasinai nusora bowi ge awa gege de ike nitinoise nowena. Yesura ni pasinai meni zebura nena amira putou na emo denu tepo wenua awa. Are na da ago ni pasinai nusora betena zebura ara tamai naso nana ena tepo wenua.  
\v 15 Tama aiso kapaire nuaita tama aiso kapai tepo nuai awa nena me amu. Ota nuai seka meni awa nena me.  
\v 16 Kotumai awa puro nowenakare. Nikare dai kotumai awa puro nowewa, are begare awa-diaire nisokare nana witiro itaise. Agoro Anutura Isreli ema me wero nowera nusokare nana dai witiro itaise.   
\p
\v 17 Zo meni noko yaya bua namore oko potaise. Na Tua Yesura bumizi owere tama nasora itawi puro nowena.   
\p
\v 18 Otao mamai naso, Tua nasokai Yesu Kristora dumi yagaba meni duba nisokarera nana itaise. Iyo.   